  "text": "Automated cell tracking. Live imaging data was analysed using custom image analysis scripts (see below and Supplementary Software 1). The exception to this was analysis of hTert-RPE1 mRuby-PCNA cells expressing GFP-53BP1, which were manually analysed using Volocity software (PerkinElmer) as we were unable to achieve reliable tracking of 53BP1 foci, and hTert-RPE1 p21-GFP cells expressing CDK2L-mRuby (CDK2 sensor [CITATION_1] ) since there was no constant nuclear signal to track reliably.",
